[2025-08-17 21:25:24][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It lifted its palm and pointed it towards the side of the volcano. Power gathered for but a moment before a blast was released, shearing off the entire side of the mountain. A blast that would have ripped Jake apart if it had ever hit him… making it clear exactly how unserious the King was.' length: 2734 characters, 518 words
