[2025-08-17 21:29:06][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Limit Break had been active at 20% from the very first Infused Powershot. In reality, it had only been minutes, but he was already starting to feel it taking its toll. Deactivating the boost wasn’t an option, as he would enter a state of weakness—a shortcut to a quick death for sure.' length: 648 characters, 115 words
