[2025-08-17 21:30:04][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'If it had been smaller spears and not freaking trees, he wouldn’t even have to dodge. The aim of the King was obviously compromised by the curse that afflicted him. This was likely also the reason why he didn’t shoot those ridiculously overpowered blasts of force.' length: 3819 characters, 698 words
