[2025-08-17 21:31:55][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Countless stars all floated around the rotting black moon. A moon that was shattered and broken, leaking out copious amounts of dark green energy. It had lost all its splendor and now carried only the feeling of corruption and decay—an omen of death incarnate.' length: 1122 characters, 203 words
