[2025-08-17 22:23:24][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'In the same vein, crafters had to push themselves too. The non-combat professions and classes had to go beyond their comfort zones and strive to improve themselves. Craft items of higher rarity or greater difficulty, maybe even craft different things. Use more expensive materials and never stagnate.' length: 1721 characters, 282 words
