[2025-08-17 22:30:02][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Duskleaf was an alchemist. Period. He had always been an alchemist and never cared much for anything else. He had mostly ignored his class, only leveling it sparingly whenever necessary. It was due to his extreme talent and dedication that he’d managed to ascend to godhood—a commitment he had believed Jake to lack.' length: 11150 characters, 2018 words
