[2025-08-17 22:31:10][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Mentally gritting his teeth, he began focusing on his body and felt the many different poisons and herbs. He needed to not focus on the pain, no matter how hard it was. He needed to focus on all the energies in him. Feel them and absorb them.' length: 957 characters, 177 words
