[2025-08-17 22:36:29][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Duskleaf opened his eyes in fright while the Viper just began laughing hysterically. It appeared that Jake found the speed of the trial too slow. Something he indeed did.' length: 4399 characters, 776 words
