[2025-08-17 22:38:20][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Landing on the ground, it caused a small earthquake. Jake just stayed there unmoving, weirdly enough, not feeling any sense of alarm or danger despite the massive, powerful form before him.' length: 1029 characters, 178 words
