[2025-08-17 22:43:46][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It was within him now. Dormant. In the end, Jake was still only E-grade. For him to absorb the power within the blood was impossible with his current strength. Yet it was still suppressed, and it would only strengthen their bond for the future.' length: 6188 characters, 1071 words
