[2025-08-17 22:44:23][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Man, those descriptions are just getting longer was his first thought. His second thought was how the skill hadn’t really changed, except for providing even more stats. He was beginning to see a trend with these Malefic Viper skills providing stats upon reaching ancient rarity. By design, no doubt. If he didn’t have his One Step Mile, he would maybe even suspect that providing stats was a hallmark of all ancient skills.' length: 1065 characters, 181 words
