[2025-08-17 22:48:39][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Currently, he only got a skill every ten levels. It was every five levels before the first class evolution, so he had a strong suspicion it would be even less than every ten levels after his next evolution. And on top of that, his biggest issue was that he often just had better skills—this very skill-picking session being one such situation.' length: 1351 characters, 233 words
