[2025-08-17 22:50:28][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'In the end, there was no contest as to which skill he would choose. The 63 bonus Wisdom alone made the Sagacity of the Malefic Viper just too tempting to pass up. He found it interesting that he would now effectively get 4 more stat points per level in his profession than otherwise stated with the skill. He had quite honestly lucked out hardcore when it came to stumbling across that Challenge Dungeon.' length: 984 characters, 179 words
