[2025-08-17 22:51:04][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It felt like hours as he was assaulted by a constant stream of information downloaded directly into him. There was so much he quite frankly couldn’t contain it all. The entire process took nearly an hour before the influx and pain subsided.' length: 240 characters, 42 words
