[2025-08-17 22:58:33][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It was a constant routine that she had done now for nearly two years. It wasn't that bad, and she got used to it. Of course, it was a bit of a downer that it was involuntary. Prison as a violent offender wasn't exactly the beacon of freedom, after all.' length: 1412 characters, 252 words
