[2025-08-17 22:59:09][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Luckily her parents were the right sort. Her mother had married into the family, and her dad had always been a bit of an outcast himself—one that didn't get better when he allowed his wife to give her a Spanish name over a more Italian one. Carmen.' length: 248 characters, 47 words
