[2025-08-17 23:00:22][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Despite it all, Carmen had tried to be her cousin's friend. Who wouldn't want to be the friend of Miss Perfect? And for the most part, her cousin appeared to accept her as her little follower. That was how her childhood went. Carmen was always the second fiddle. That was, until she turned eighteen and was introduced to an entirely new world: boxing.' length: 351 characters, 63 words
