[2025-08-17 23:00:46][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It turned out that while Carmen was a dunce with a book, she was really good at hitting people. Impressively so. She began to build up her own self-confidence and finally find herself. She got new friends and a boyfriend, and finally she was her own person—something she came to learn her cousin didn't like.' length: 308 characters, 55 words
