[2025-08-17 23:01:38][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It was a simple favor. "Come help clean my car." Thinking back, it was actually more an order than a request. But stupidly, she had gone to help her hopeless cousin. She had helped clean it with her cousin standing to the side on her phone. This day, however, Carmen had decided to stand up for herself.' length: 3251 characters, 590 words
