[2025-08-17 23:02:15][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'Carmen didn't want to go—of course she didn't—but she was made to go anyway. The wedding was to be perfect, the entire family of both the bride and groom there. As her father had recently gotten promoted to a high position, she knew the only reason they were invited was to brag about how great their family was.' length: 980 characters, 183 words
