[2025-08-17 23:14:34][DEBUG][root] Chapter 'It was joked about that Eron could see if a person was sick just by looking at them, which Eron never found particularly funny. Because he could. A fact he had learned very early on in his life, and he knew only he could see those small sparks—a secret he had come to hide. It was his gift, one he would not waste.' length: 970 characters, 174 words
[2025-08-17 23:14:34][DEBUG][urllib3.connectionpool] Starting new HTTP connection (1): localhost:1234
